{
  "stem": "26142.14",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But for us, for me personally, we were there before, and we knew some of it, but we didn't know in this one and a half years since we were there before that it was such a total-- total destruction.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After a few days when we arrived in Stanislau, the commander started sending out certain groups with Hungarian escorts to do certain works.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] One group was sent out that worked in-- in-- where they cleaned-- they cleaned carcasses for leather from cattle.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was very, very dirty work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I want to-- I want to-- I want to fulfill the promise that I promised this girl and what I saw in there the first week when we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I have to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is just one page. 'One day, I fell into a group of five soldiers of our [INAUDIBLE] escorted us to a four-story building in the city of Stanislau.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The building was an officer's club for Hungarian and German officers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The building had no elevator, only stairs, and our job was to wash and clean the whole stairway, and also some rooms-- to wash the floors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As we reached the top floor, we saw in the rooms lots of young women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't catch on right away what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We, the Carpathian boys, we spoke among ourselves Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When one of the girls overheard us, that we talked in Yiddish, she broke out in a lament in tears, and she started to talk to us and tell us that they are simply here for pure rape for these animals.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And after sometimes, these girls disappear and they never come back here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They're not even allowed to go down to the third floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
